review 1:
Gede is probably the most amazing host on this island and his staff as well. We‚Äôre happy to have met him and he became a great friend.This little oasis is a gem you shouldn‚Äôt miss in Bali. Wish we could have stayed more.

name: Simpang Gading Lawar Celuk
address: Jl. Raya Celuk No.24X, Celuk, Kec. Sukawati, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80582, Indonesia
review 1: The owner and stuffs are really nice and the food was amazing.  The store closed at 9 but they let us dine after 9 since there are no other restaurants around.  Totally recommend it for local food
review 2: So tasty, love it. And the best part was it's cozy place where I can stretch my legs and chill from the heat of the sun. Great place for travellers near celuk area
review 3: Delicious food but expensive and way of the standard price for the same type of food and the same set restaurants I ever visited. You can pay less and get more at another place.
review 4: Excellent food and restaurant for a very good price. Highly recommended for people interested in local hangouts
review 5: Best local pork rice dish ever.

We come here every time we are visiting Ubud and surrounds. Well deserved 5 stars. Well done!!
review 2: Very beautiful room, gardens, swimming pool, Friendly staff and tasty food. The gaid is very friendly he organised the tour for us to visit the beautiful place, s in Bali.We recommend.
review 3: Stayed here for 2 nights with our friends. We had the most amazing time here, Gede‚Äôs an amazing host and always go above and beyond to make sure that we have an enjoyable stay. Lovely staff, super clean and well maintained. Would highly recommend staying here. Great location, 20mins by motorbike/car to Ubud and Denpasar.
